name: Cardigan, T-Shirt & Leggings Set
description:
This cardigan, tshirt and leggings set is the perfect outfit for baby during the Autumn months. Pair with knitted booties for a complete look.
  • Cardigan: Hood, striped lining. Wrap detail front with button fastening.
  • tshirt: Placement print tshirt, long sleeved. Nickel-free popper back fastening.
  • Leggings: Elasticated waistband, all over print legging.
    Material: Jacket: Main: 100% Cotton Lining: 100% Cotton Top: 100% Cotton Bottoms: 100% Cotton
    Care Instructions:
    • 40 degree reduced cycle
    • do not bleach
    • tumble dry on a low heat
    • 1 dot iron
    • do not dry clean
    • wash dark colours separately
